release_note: Fixed a bug that caused the app to crash when loading videos. Fixed a bug that allowed the transition period to be longer than the video length.
When selecting an image the end position could not be selected up to 3 seconds but it was extended to 300 seconds.
The aspect ratio can be changed. The aspect ratio can be selected from 2: 1 16: 9 4: 3 and 1: 1.
Bug fix that can not select video from file on iPad.
The volume selection range has been expanded to 0 300 .
Fixed a bug that the resolution is lowered when saving the edited video.
You can add images as well as videos.
Added File to video selection. You can select image files from various cloud services. Added Camera to video selection. Dark mode Light mode is fixed but ...
Fixed a bug where thumbnails of additional videos were not displayed.
Provide reverse play mode of video.
Improvement in screen design. Playback speed up to 10 times.
only supports iOS8 and later versions. and bugs fix.
Supported the email message and facebook.
